## 3. How to Deploy & Verify

1. Run the compilation build task:
   ```powershell
   npm run build
   ```
2. Launch the PRISM server or run locally in dev:
   ```powershell
   npm run dev
   ```
3. Navigate to the **Logs & Debug** tab to see:
   - **🎫 Active Support Tickets Queue**: Open detailed folding panels, run manual resolutions, submit custom tickets, and check SQLite database storage integrity.
   - **🖥️ Live Operator Console**: Live stdout/stderr WebSocket logs flowing with custom filters and pause capabilities.
   - **⚡ Connected MCP Servers**: High-fidelity, real-time polling panel showing online MCP adapter systems.
